  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n \n<center><table>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"R.gif\"/><font> <b>Burbank\nwith a Baedeker: Bleistein with a Cigar</b></font>\n<hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>This poem is probably Eliot's most allusionary poem; or,\nif not the most allusionary, certainly the most selfconscious in the way\nother texts are evoked - in no other poem meaning has become so dependent\non association and reading. </font>\n</p><p><i><font>reference topics</font></i>\n<br/> \n</p><table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"introduction.htm\">introduction</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"publication_data.htm\"><img src=\"arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><font><a href=\"publication_data.htm\">full\npublication history</a></font></td>\n<td><a href=\"publication_data.htm\"><img src=\"arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><font>discussion of <a href=\"title_A.htm\">the\ntitle</a></font></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Bleistein.htm\">Bleistein</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><font><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\">back to \"Burbank\" </a></font></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table></center>\n",
  "text": "Burbank with a Baedeker: Bleistein with a Cigar This poem is probably Eliot's most allusionary poem; or, if not the most allusionary, certainly the most selfconscious in the way other texts are evoked - in no other poem meaning has become so dependent on association and reading. reference topics introduction full publication history discussion of the title Bleistein back to \"Burbank\"",
